==============
 Installation
==============

 Simply add the jab.py file to /usr/bin or add a symlink to it



================
 Usage Examples
================

 jab create controller search

This adds a new controller to the controllers directory and adds 
search folders to the view and template directories. It then adds
an index view and index template to them.


 jab create view search missing

This adds a view to the view/search folder named "missing.js". It 
then adds a template to the template/search directory with the
same name.


 jab create template search foo

This adds a template to template/search named "foo.html"
